  devicekit-power-014.ebuild:
  amd64 stable, bug #314899

  11 Apr 2010; Raúl Porcel <armin76@gentoo.org> devicekit-power-009.ebuild,
  devicekit-power-014.ebuild:
  Add ~alpha/~ia64/~sparc

  11 Mar 2010; Nirbheek Chauhan <nirbheek@gentoo.org>
  devicekit-power-009.ebuild, -devicekit-power-011.ebuild,
  -devicekit-power-012.ebuild, -devicekit-power-012-r1.ebuild,
  -files/devicekit-power-012-hibernate-encrypted-swap.patch,
  -devicekit-power-013.ebuild, devicekit-power-014.ebuild:
  Remove old versions, fix ACPI test to be restricted to amd64/x86

*devicekit-power-014 (23 Feb 2010)

  23 Feb 2010; Gilles Dartiguelongue <eva@gentoo.org>
  +devicekit-power-014.ebuild:
  Version bump. Import bsd backend, segfault fixes.

*devicekit-power-013 (11 Dec 2009)

  11 Dec 2009; Nirbheek Chauhan <nirbheek@gentoo.org>
  +devicekit-power-013.ebuild:
  Bump to 013; NEWS says this is the last release since the project has been
  renamed to 'upower'

*devicekit-power-012-r1 (16 Nov 2009)

  16 Nov 2009; Gilles Dartiguelongue <eva@gentoo.org>
  devicekit-power-011.ebuild, devicekit-power-012.ebuild,
  +devicekit-power-012-r1.ebuild,
  +files/devicekit-power-012-hibernate-encrypted-swap.patch:
  Fix encrypted swap detection, bug #292090. Use slotted virtual/libusb
  dependency in all ebuilds.

*devicekit-power-012 (01 Nov 2009)

  01 Nov 2009; Gilles Dartiguelongue <eva@gentoo.org>
  +devicekit-power-012.ebuild:
  Version bump. Disable static libs, review missing dtds in DEPEND, add
  missing DOCS. Do not hibernate on encrypted swap and bugfixes.

*devicekit-power-011 (29 Oct 2009)

  29 Oct 2009; Gilles Dartiguelongue <eva@gentoo.org>
  +devicekit-power-011.ebuild, metadata.xml:
  Initial ebuild for GNOME 2.28.

  08 Sep 2009; Mike Auty <ikelos@gentoo.org> devicekit-power-009.ebuild:
  Making CONFIG_CHECK non-fatal for userland ebuilds, see bug 283320.

*devicekit-power-009 (08 Aug 2009)

  08 Aug 2009; Gilles Dartiguelongue <eva@gentoo.org>
  +files/devicekit-power-007-maintainer-cflags.patch,
  +devicekit-power-009.ebuild,
